@biharitomi thanks! looks like this is not affecting direct CM requests. This is a direct call to CM, notice there is no response from the server (not even 403). If this was going through the patched nginx code we would have seen 403.

When the request goes through Knox we return 403 (nginx patch code)

Which makes me conclude this patch works as expected. Let me know your thoughts.

